### Tuist ###
# The Xcode project/workspace are generated by `tuist generate` — never committed.
*.xcodeproj
*.xcworkspace

# Tuist-derived files and managed dependencies (any depth).
Derived/
**/Tuist/.build/
graph.dot

### Web (Next.js marketing site) ###
# Dependencies and build output. The site is a static export: `npm run build`
# emits web/out/, which is generated and never committed.
/web/node_modules/
/web/.next/
/web/out/
/web/build/
/web/coverage/

# Generated by Next.js on build.
/web/next-env.d.ts
/web/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets and deploy state.
/web/.env*
/web/.vercel
/web/*.pem

# Logs
/web/npm-debug.log*
/web/yarn-debug.log*
/web/yarn-error.log*
/web/.pnpm-debug.log*

### Project ###
# Local task tracking (markdown issues) is not committed.
/tasks/
